                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae NeMo Framework.&nbsp;<div>To protect your system, clone or update this software to version 2.6.2 or later from <a href=\"https://github.com/NVIDIA/NeMo\">NVIDIA/NeMo Framework</a> on NVIDIA GitHub or <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/nemo-toolkit/\">pypi</a>.</div>",
